Wall Street Plaza is an iconic landmark in the heart of Orlando‚Äôs Downtown Entertainment District. The venue has up to a 3,500-person capacity. For the last 30 years, Wall Street Plaza has been the home of downtown‚Äôs biggest events. The brick road that is in the shadow of the historic Angebilt Hotel provides an intimate setting for the ultimate concert experience. The guest experience is enhanced by the 8 bars and restaurants that line the street on both sides.
Family Friendly
With eight of the most unique venues & restaurants in the heart of Downtown Orlando, Wall Street Plaza is the place for the best in family-friendly daytime events, block parties, sporting events, and live music concerts. We have regular partnerships with The Orlando Magic and Orlando City Soccer for the biggest viewing parties in the city. Whether it‚Äôs the World Cup viewing parties or the Marathon Race for Olympic qualification with world-class athletes, our central location guarantees the best seat. With our monthly food markets and other daytime special events, Wall Street Plaza provides fun for the whole family.
Concerts
Our goal is to bring exclusive multicultural entertainment to Downtown Orlando, hosting live music and entertainment as diverse as the community that surrounds us: country, R&B, EDM, Top 40, and Latin.
Large Celebrations
Wall Street Plaza is already known as the place to be for St. Patty‚Äôs Day, Cinco de Mayo, Halloween, and New Year‚Äôs Eve Parties. Over 30,000 people visit Wall Street for these 4 events every year. We also kicked off our quarterly Downtown Concert Series with our Labor Day Weekend Block Parties. In collaboration with Citrus Sports, we created an incredible 3-day event with 2 stages and 11 different Country Music and cover band artists that was enjoyed by over 22,000 people.
Food
Enjoy some of the best Mexican food at our restaurant Wall Street Cantina. 2 more restaurant concepts coming soon.
